    "description": "Devil Can Beat is a rogue-like rhythm game.<br><br>Attack or dash on every beat to beat your enemies.<br><br>Each level features its own music, requiring you to adapt to different beats that are added as you progress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153010/extras/470784e978f10bf3e1c53232ae92bee7.poster.avif?t=1724172616\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153010/extras/470784e978f10bf3e1c53232ae92bee7.webm?t=1724172616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153010/extras/470784e978f10bf3e1c53232ae92bee7.mp4?t=1724172616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br>Explore the dungeons: Every dungeon’s beat is different; clear dungeons to reach bosses.<br><br>Collect Orbs: Orbs can be quite useful in defeating your enemies. Collect them to upgrade your shield, attack power, and dash range.<br><br>Upgrade Your Character: At the end of every level, you can choose between 3 different power-ups that fit your playstyle.<br><br>Come Back Stronger: Each loss paved the way for a powerful demon. Use permanent upgrades to come back stronger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153010/extras/22085522eb3c325e5a1115057f0aea72.poster.avif?t=1724172616\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153010/extras/22085522eb3c325e5a1115057f0aea72.webm?t=1724172616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153010/extras/22085522eb3c325e5a1115057f0aea72.mp4?t=1724172616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>&quot;Dissonance is evil; rhythm is lethal.&quot;</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153010/extras/295e31ef0c39c8b0266e659bd78805c9.avif?t=1724172616\" width=616 height=180 /></span>",
